data.text:
Age 73

Preceded in death by parents, Janis and Austra Mende. Survived by husband, Bill; children, Joseph Dineen (Yasaman) and Anne Dineen (Todd Small); grandchildren, Addison and Avari Small; brother, Eric Mende (Barb); sister-in-law, Rita Stovie.

MEMORIAL MASS: Tuesday, July 31st, 10am, St. Joan of Arc Catholic Church, 3122 S. 74th St. with a luncheon immediately following Mass.

In lieu of flowers memorials are suggested to St. Joan of Arc School or Holy Name School.
